metadata.name: Sun Tiger 001
metadata.description:
Here is "Sun Tiger". I invented this Tiger in 2016, to represent Strength, Hope, Reasoning, Justice, Loyalty, and of course the Sun which is the symbol of Loyalty. "Sun Tiger" is able to manifest itself anytime and anywhere, even through darkness. "Sun Tiger ", is more or less hidden in every human being! It only presents itself when one is serene and rid of hatred. He is there to protect you on your right path to justice and especially when Ethics becomes your Strength...
Now enjoy with this NFT
